name: Lokah
description:
All universes merge, Into the forever
of now. Unimagined realms find me,
On the playground of all gods, Asking
new questions. I thrive on riddles,
Decisive, eternal, Not needing
forgiveness, Or asking permission to
be. Existence honors my light and my
shadows. Blissfully caught into
oneness, I am all that is and all of it is
me. Written by REBELLICCA - 2021
*lokah (Sanskrit): location, realm, all
universes existing now
